name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-the-jarvis-island-2004
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 6 sites at Jarvis Island in March from the NOAA vessel Oscar Elton Sette (OES04-04). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
